{"tid":2138478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TikTok母公司「字節跳動」跳船將會引發連鎖反應，撕裂中國科網巨頭","createTime":"2020-08-03T15:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T15:30:18.000Z","uid":359123,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e8cba0eab3e0f0ce737be918ada51a557d09c8","tid":2138478,"uid":359123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"TikTok作為新興社交媒體影響力異常巨大，係少數真正具聲望同影響力既中國企業，另一個就係華為。但身為中國公司既原罪令佢必須遵守中共既規則。習近平不停強調舉國體制同政府主導，要管曬所有企業，而哩種意識型態令所有做緊國際生意既中國公司失去自己私下既斡旋空間。全世界冇人會信中國企業係獨立行事，哩樣係習近平自己造成。<br />\n<br />\n有D企業例如華為本來就under中共軍方，好自然會跟黨走。但會唔會有部分民企 (相對而言) 係不滿哩種角力而選擇投奔自由世界呢？<br />\n<br />\n近期既蛛絲螞跡判斷出字節跳動 (特別佢老細張一鳴)係非常刻意同中共保持距離：<br />\n<br />\n首先最近期既新聞，字節跳動要搬總部，仲要選擇目前關係極為惡劣既英國 - 香港前宗主國。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-bytedance-britain/tiktok-owners-will-relocate-to-london-from-beijing-sun-newspaper-says-idUSKBN24Z0IE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-bytedance-britain%2Ftiktok-owners-will-relocate-to-london-from-beijing-sun-newspaper-says-idUSKBN24Z0IE&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=f734feab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-bytedance-britain%2Ftiktok-owners-will-relocate-to-london-from-beijing-sun-newspaper-says-idUSKBN24Z0IE&h=756f1599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-bytedance-britain/tiktok-owners-will-relocate-to-london-from-beijing-sun-newspaper-says-idUSKBN24Z0IE</a><br />\n<br />\n字節跳動傾賣美國TikTok俾Microsoft。張一鳴幾唔認同出售都好，係佢眼中只要有得賣都好過因為中美衝突將成間公司毀於一旦。係小粉紅同戰狼派眼中哩D係投美份子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/2020/08/02/microsoft-to-continue-discussions-on-potential-tiktok-purchase-in-the-united-states/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2F2020%2F08%2F02%2Fmicrosoft-to-continue-discussions-on-potential-tiktok-purchase-in-the-united-states%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=e7cc169a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/2020/08/02/microsoft-to-continue-discussions-on-potential-tiktok-purchase-in-the-united-states/</a><br />\n<br />\nTik Tok於國安法生效後後立即退出香港市場。一方面固然要國際展示Tik Tok國際版係獨立經營，但再獨立都好，Google都未話quit ，你就第一時間彈出黎。咁敏感既事身為母公司既字節跳動唔可能事前唔知。一間中國公司反國安法，中共有冇可能唔嬲？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2020-07-07/tiktok-to-stop-operating-in-hong-kong-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2020-07-07%2Ftiktok-to-stop-operating-in-hong-kong-video&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=38b74d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2020-07-07/tiktok-to-stop-operating-in-hong-kong-video</a><br />\n<br />\n張一鳴態度就更可圈可點。小粉紅搵到佢12年既貼文瘋狂批鬥：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8pdHBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8pdHBo.jpg&h=caa1d9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官媒態度亦都非常反常。胡錫進戰狼左咁耐，一時話整核彈，一時又話出兵印度，今次竟然話中方反制很有限。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4749116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F4749116&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=3d3c6e8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/4749116</a><br />\n<br />\n字節跳動依家似係採取同中共維持適當關係但積極build up國際基礎，例如最近放風會係中港兩地上市做緩衝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-bytedance-ipo-exclusive/exclusive-tiktok-owner-bytedance-considers-listing-china-business-in-hong-kong-or-shanghai-sources-idUSKCN24W0OL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-bytedance-ipo-exclusive%2Fexclusive-tiktok-owner-bytedance-considers-listing-china-business-in-hong-kong-or-shanghai-sources-idUSKCN24W0OL&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=dffc8513\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-bytedance-ipo-exclusive%2Fexclusive-tiktok-owner-bytedance-considers-listing-china-business-in-hong-kong-or-shanghai-sources-idUSKCN24W0OL&h=fee611ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-bytedance-ipo-exclusive/exclusive-tiktok-owner-bytedance-considers-listing-china-business-in-hong-kong-or-shanghai-sources-idUSKCN24W0OL</a><br />\n<br />\n中共可能本身似乎都對字節跳動相當不滿，可能社交APP係佢地眼中都唔算咩核心產業，所以非常低調。但牽一髮而動全身。會有幾多中國企業跟風撤出呢？黎緊Trump好快要開騰訊刀，騰訊會唔會用字節跳動類似既策略以保全自身？<br />\n<br />\n根據Pompeo既講法，白宮將中共，而唔係中國定調為敵人，現時對科技對中國科網巨頭既打擊唔係單純既摧毀哩堆公司，反而係希望係以表面既制裁去作出產業同資本吸納，係國際社會既規則下將佢地收攬，從而將中共既內部影響力切割出去。<br />\n<br />\n中共係外資退出中國既現實情況下又要面對內部科網企業因面臨制裁而必須脫離自身既絕對控制，一係就中共強行接管所有公司迎接高科技產業同國際社會全面脫勾、一係就睇住一堆中國公司撤出中國。兩者既下場都係冇退路。<br />\n<br />\n香港一直好多人話要對準政權，其實美國人先最精於此道。"},{"pid":"81f16ecbfab454f8a4aab0427dff46c4b048d694","tid":2138478,"uid":275865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ec748a7df7ae29fc0b22ccfe30b27497b72442","tid":2138478,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"好圖好文<br />\n推下先"},{"pid":"24919c1d496755d68d1b42bc9d2122242023f6cf","tid":2138478,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">中共可能本身似乎都對字節跳動相當不滿，可能社交APP係佢地眼中都唔算咩核心產業，所以非常低調。</span></strong>但牽一髮而動全身。會有幾多中國企業跟風撤出呢？黎緊Trump好快要開騰訊刀，騰訊會唔會用字節跳動類似既策略以保全自身？<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n從大數據+misinformation策略黎講好重要，可以分析敵國政情加撕裂敵國"},{"pid":"4ce572962f6c7a6bc7cfe89f525b7273ca40d629","tid":2138478,"uid":359123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24919c1d496755d68d1b42bc9d2122242023f6cf","tid":2138478,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">中共可能本身似乎都對字節跳動相當不滿，可能社交APP係佢地眼中都唔算咩核心產業，所以非常低調。</span></strong>但牽一髮而動全身。會有幾多中國企業跟風撤出呢？黎緊Trump好快要開騰訊刀，騰訊會唔會用字節跳動類似既策略以保全自身？<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n從大數據+misinformation策略黎講好重要，可以分析敵國政情加撕裂敵國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"的確係。<br />\n但係中共班內參明唔明係另一回事。"},{"pid":"3da0c165348f6cb3722e794e72ed0da34ca7ef0e","tid":2138478,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"行到依一步 必然會繼續走強硬路線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c930407fe6875c58fb6872274a208967792ac37","tid":2138478,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7822ebe04ec9444e004ab2fae0428b14195239","tid":2138478,"uid":36724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"邊個科網巨頭唔係靠中共比個經營權佢先上位"},{"pid":"cfcc4b129db77dd9c7d9d916c8926e0ce096ab15","tid":2138478,"uid":363147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"佢兩個APP都係毒瘤中嘅毒瘤<br />\n大家熟悉嘅抖陰<br />\n仲有大陸假新聞真propaganda之最：今日頭條<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/张一鸣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%80%E9%B8%A3&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=e169ecd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/张一鸣</a>"}]}